      "content": "it's not just about being \"overwhelmed.\" it's like... there's no way back from this. the debt is permanent. the reputation is dead. i look at my life and i don't even see a person anymore, just a set of mistakes. i feel like i've already died, i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up. i feel like the most logical thing would be to just stop the noise.",
